oregano garnish on rustic table shot with selective focus" loading="eager" srcSet="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_80.webp 80w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_160.webp 160w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_240.webp 240w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_360.webp 360w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_480.webp 480w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_640.webp 640w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_720.webp 720w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_960.webp 960w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_1080.webp 1080w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_1440.webp 1440w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/40/23738384/3/ratio3x2_1920.webp 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 920px) 80vw, (max-width: 1320px) 50vw, 720px" style="aspect-ratio:3 / 2" class="x100 opc bgpc ofcv bgscv block to03 y100 o0 noscript:o100 mnh0"/><div style="aspect-ratio:3 / 2;background-image:url(data:image/jpeg;base64,)" class="x100 opc bgpc ofcv bgscv block to03 y100 o100 bgrn abs pen fill noscript:o0"></div></div><figcaption class="ff-fontG fw-fontG fs-fontG lh12 ps1 fs14 f fdc g2 rel pt8 px20 sm:px0"><span class="ya"><span class="re6bgoq n4l52un ff-fontG fw-fontG fs-fontG lh12 ps1 fs14 c-gray700">spaghetti and meatballs with oregano garnish on rustic table shot with selective focus</span></span><span class="ff-fontG fw-fontG fs-fontG lh12 ps1 fs12 c-gray600 mt2 mr48">Getty</span></figcaption></figure><div class="re6bgoq d1uy5mhj ff-fontJ fw-fontJ fs-fontJ lh18 ps32 fs18"><p>In the U.S., the birthplace of fast food, Americans eat fewer than 70 percent of their meals at home and less than a third of American families eat meals together more than twice a week, according to Emory University. This fact, together with the obesity epidemic, points toward a need for fundamental change in American food culture. A collective return to the home-cooked meal may offer significant health and social advantages over current trends.</p></div><div class="pt16 mb32 sy16 bb bt b-gray300"><div><p class="ff-fontE fw-fontE fs-fontE lh12 fs12 f aic jcc ttu">Advertisement</p><p class="ff-fontG fw-fontG fs-fontG lh12 fs12 f aic jcc">Article continues below this ad</p></div><div class="tac mb16 sm:mnh300px" data-block-type="ad" data-small-id="A300" data-large-id="Inline-1" data-unit="hnp-weekand.com/article_dtc"></div></div><div class="re6bgoq d1uy5mhj ff-fontJ fw-fontJ fs-fontJ lh18 ps32 fs18"><h2>Food Allergies and Sensitivities</h2></div><div class="mb32"><div class="rel block x1px y1px vh bgt abs"><img aria-hidden="true" alt="" loading="eager" srcSet="https://cdn-channels-pixel.ex.co/events/0012000001fxZm9AAE?integrationType=DEFAULT&amp;template=design%2Farticle%2Fplatypus.tpl 1w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 920px) 80vw, (max-width: 1320px) 50vw, 720px" style="aspect-ratio:1 / 1" class="opc bgpc ofcv bgscv block to03 y100 o0 noscript:o100 mnh0"/></div><div id="d1cd7daa-7eff-43a4-a9c9-df76c45ea607"></div></div><div class="re6bgoq d1uy5mhj ff-fontJ fw-fontJ fs-fontJ lh18 ps32 fs18"><p>Cooking your own meals affords you the peace of mind that goes along with having complete control over the type and quality of ingredients in your meals and the degree of cleanliness that goes into their preparation. Preparing meals at home allows you to easily accommodate family members or guests who have allergies or food intolerences, some of which, such as peanut and shellfish allergies, can lead to life-threatening emergencies. Gluten, a protein found in wheat, rye and barley is difficult for many people to digest and causes a serious autoimmune response in some. Awareness of gluten intolerance has improved in recent years. However, since wheat is pervasive in the western diet it can be a challenge to find restaurants willing or able to accommodate this dietary requirement.</p></div><div data-block-type="inlinerecirculation" class="pb32"><div class="f fdc sy16"><div class="ff-fontE fw-fontE fs-fontE lh12 fs18 bt bw2 ttc pt8"><h2 class="wsn">More For You</h2></div><div><div class="f fdc jcb"><article class="grid col1-min"><div class="grid sy8 mb8 mr8 col1 row1"><h2 class="c-black ff-fontC fw-fontC fs-fontC lh13 fs16 sm:fs18"><a class="tdn hover:o70 td300" data-link="spa" href="/healthy-living/article/weight-loss-elderly-even-good-appetite-18024644.php">Weight Loss in Elderly Even With Good Appetite</a></h2></div><div class="grid sy8 col1span2 row2"></div><div class="block col2 row1 ml8 x78px xs:x100px sm:x140px lg:x78px x90px sm:x112px"><a data-link="spa" href="/healthy-living/article/weight-loss-elderly-even-good-appetite-18024644.php"><div class="rel x100 block"><img title="Weight Loss in Elderly Even With Good Appetite" alt="Variety of avocado toasts with fresh radish cress, mushrooms and persimmon. Plant based colorful vegan snack on gray background viewed from above" loading="lazy" srcSet="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_80.webp 80w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_160.webp 160w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_240.webp 240w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_360.webp 360w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_480.webp 480w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_640.webp 640w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_720.webp 720w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_960.webp 960w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_1080.webp 1080w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_1440.webp 1440w, https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/ratio3x2_1920.webp 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 240px, (max-width: 480px) 360px, 480px" style="aspect-rat