er than 70 percent of their meals at home and less than a third of American families eat meals together more than twice a week, according to Emory University. This fact, together with the obesity epidemic, points toward a need for fundamental change in American food culture. A collective return to the home-cooked meal may offer significant health and social advantages over current trends."},"_owner":null}}},{"__typename":"AdBlock","type":"ad","params":{"layout":null,"code":null,"small":"A300","large":"Inline-1","showInlineAdLabel":true,"adUnitPath":"hnp-weekand.com/article_dtc"}},{"__typename":"TextBlock","type":"text","params":{"layout":"","html1":"\u003ch2\u003eFood Allergies and Sensitivities\u003c/h2\u003e","isDropcap":false,"serializedReact":{"type":"h2","key":null,"ref":null,"props":{"children":"Food Allergies and Sensitivities"},"_owner":null}}},{"__typename":"ZoneBlock","type":"zone","params":{"layout":null,"embed":{"__type":"thirdPartyFreeformEmbed","__id":"exco","__element":{"tag":"div","attributes":{"id":"d1cd7daa-7eff-43a4-a9c9-df76c45ea607"}},"__src":"https://player.ex.co/player/","__ping":"https://cdn-channels-pixel.ex.co/events/0012000001fxZm9AAE?integrationType=DEFAULT\u0026template=","__data":{"articleId":"d1cd7daa-7eff-43a4-a9c9-df76c45ea607","channelId":"04149991-21bb-4b67-b7af-3808c8785bb1"}}}},{"__typename":"TextBlock","type":"text","params":{"layout":"","html1":"\u003cp\u003eCooking your own meals affords you the peace of mind that goes along with having complete control over the type and quality of ingredients in your meals and the degree of cleanliness that goes into their preparation. Preparing meals at home allows you to easily accommodate family members or guests who have allergies or food intolerences, some of which, such as peanut and shellfish allergies, can lead to life-threatening emergencies. Gluten, a protein found in wheat, rye and barley is difficult for many people to digest and causes a serious autoimmune response in some. Awareness of gluten intolerance has improved in recent years. However, since wheat is pervasive in the western diet it can be a challenge to find restaurants willing or able to accommodate this dietary requirement.\u003c/p\u003e","isDropcap":false,"serializedReact":{"type":"p","key":null,"ref":null,"props":{"children":"Cooking your own meals affords you the peace of mind that goes along with having complete control over the type and quality of ingredients in your meals and the degree of cleanliness that goes into their preparation. Preparing meals at home allows you to easily accommodate family members or guests who have allergies or food intolerences, some of which, such as peanut and shellfish allergies, can lead to life-threatening emergencies. Gluten, a protein found in wheat, rye and barley is difficult for many people to digest and causes a serious autoimmune response in some. Awareness of gluten intolerance has improved in recent years. However, since wheat is pervasive in the western diet it can be a challenge to find restaurants willing or able to accommodate this dietary requirement."},"_owner":null}}},{"__typename":"RelatedStoriesBlock","type":"relatedStories","params":{"layout":null,"ipid":"","header":"","items":[{"url":"/healthy-living/article/weight-loss-elderly-even-good-appetite-18024644.php","title":"Weight Loss in Elderly Even With Good Appetite","excerpt":"Older adults can experience weight loss even if they seem to eat well and have a good...","abstract":"Older adults can experience weight loss even if they seem to eat well and have a good appetite. Reasons for weight loss range from loose dentures to the onset of dementia or other cognitive changes.","displayedDate":"2014-06-25 15:27:00","authorName":"","authors":null,"eyebrow":null,"image":{"url":"https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/32/43/35/23738235/3/rawImage.jpg","b64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":2048,"height":1365,"caption":{"plain":"Variety of avocado toasts with fresh radish cress, mushrooms a